				<td colspan="2"><span>Bard slows are mitigated to the same percentage as any other slow.  In other words, if a shaman slow is mitigated by 50%, so is RoT.  
<br />

<br />
If your brass mod is greater than 2.3 (or is it 2.4?), you'll stop getting the mitigation messages.  If you want to see the messages again once you get IM3, unequip your epic or brass mod item when you land slow.
<br />

<br />
If you need the data, I'll dig up the other threads where this was discussed.
<br />

<br />
Calli</span></td>
